children.subject: I am a freshman in L&S, and there are open reserved seats for L&S freshmen in EE16B according to the Course Catalog, but I was put on the waitlist. How should I resolve this bug?

history.content:
If you are attempting to enroll into a CompSci class and see an error message saying the wait list isn't available and you cannot enroll, please try enrolling again after 7:00pm tonight.

There is a bug in the system that is impacting our classes. When I make changes to the enrollment capacities for a class, it closes enrollment for the class until after the wait list processes in the background.

I have reported this to SIS Help and am waiting for them to help resolve the issue. 

Cindy Conners

CS Enrollment Manager
